misc: Hello, Oak Ridge,TN.  Although we can appreciate your entrepreneurial skills, Girl Scouts of the USA has an internet sales policy that states, "Sales on the Internet of any products sold in "council-sponsored product sales," such as Girl Scout Cookies, may not be conducted by anyone at any time."  As a Girl Scout you must comply with the policy of the national organization and upon receipt of this message we are asking you to remove any and all information concerning Girl Scout cookies.  Thank you for your cooperation in this matter.  [private], Director, Trademark and Licensing, Girl Scouts of the USA January 7, 2002
